name: FNF music battle coloring mod
description:
FNF music battle coloring mod to color all characters of Friday Night Funkin.
Friday Night coloring page for you to enjoy in your free time.
All characters are available now : (Tabi, Boyfriend, Girlfriend, Bopeebo, Miku, Chainsaw, Pico, Daddy Dearest, Skid and Pump, Monster, Senpai, Tankman, Cassette Girl, Hank J. Wimbleton).

This Friday night funkin coloring book game is the best that you can find to color FNF pages.

Do not forget to share with your friends.
